      "utterance": "对的，Vault和Aave Pool都挂在TransactionQueue下。流程是Vault先调用getReserveData从Aave获取liquidityRate和APY数据，然后在内部计算所有资产的APY。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "YieldVaultMultiAsset",
