      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画出了User触发triggerYieldSnapshot到Vault，以及Vault查询Aave并返回数据的步骤。接下来是RSC组件介入吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
